text: Akhtaruzzaman is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Gazipur-3. ==Career== Akhtaruzzaman was elected to parliament from Gazipur-3 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1996. He is the chairman of Gazipur District council. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
